        <span class='bookTitle'>Majiayao Culture</span> artifacts were first discovered in Gansu in 1923.
        Their range included the Upper Yellow River Basin in Qinghai and Gansu. 
        The picture below shows a pot with a string design from the <span class='bookTitle'>Majiayao Culture</span>.
      </p>
